 <body ><br><h1 class="pHead1" >
assert_quiescent_state
</h1>    
<a name="wp3692169"> </a><p class="pBody" >
Ensures that the value of a specified state expression equals a corresponding check value if a specified sample event has transitioned to TRUE.  </p>    <div align="left" class="tbl">
<table border="0">
  <caption></caption>
  <tr align="left" valign="top">    <td><a name="wp3692186"> </a><div class="pCellBodyLeft" >
