  <pre class="pCode2" >
</pre>    
<p class="pCodeShiftBottom"></p>
<a name="wp3745650"> </a><p class="pBody" >
Ensures that whenever <code class="cCodeBody">end_of_transaction</code> asserts at the completion of each transaction, the value of <code class="cCodeBody">transaction_state</code> is &#8216;TR_IDLE (if prev_tr is &#8216;TR_READ) or &#8216;TR_WAIT (otherwise).  </p>    <div align="left"><img src="images/ovl_checkers86.gif" height="118" width="480" border="0" vspace="0" hspace="100" />  </div>	
